jobs_results.description:
We are looking for an iOS developer responsible for the development and maintenance of applications aimed at a range of iOS devices including mobile phones and tablet computers. Your primary focus will be development of iOS applications and their integration with back-end services. You will be working alongside other engineers and developers working on different layers of the infrastructure.

You’ll Be Responsible For
• Design, build and maintain the next generation of IOS Applications;
• Collaborate with the design team for new application features, identifying and fixing application bottlenecks, maintaining the core code, and updating applications published on the App Store;
• Create functional, attractive applications that perfectly meet the needs of the user;
• Ensuring quality and performance of the application to specifications;
• Participation in the planning and organization of the development process
• Support and mentor junior developers;

Must Have
• 1-2 years experience of iOS Development;
• Experience working with SwiftUI, Objective-C, Xcode;
• Experience with iOS frameworks such as Core Data, Core Animation, etc;
• Proficient at utilizing iOS databases;
• Understanding of Apple’s design principles and interface guidelines;
• Understanding of OOP, SOLID principles and architectural patterns;
• Understanding of code versioning tools, such as Git, Mercurial or SVN;
• Communication, mentoring, creative thinking and problem-solving skills;
• Knowledge of English at Upper-Intermediate level;
• Willingness to work on-site at normal work hours.

Nice To Have
• Experience with HTML5 & CSS, MySQL, and JavaScript;
• Familiarity with iOS back-end services and Apple’s design principles;
• Experience with Git, Mercurial or SVN;
• Knowledge of other web technologies and UI/UX standards;

What We Offer
• Long-term job in a cozy office in the company of many skilled associates
• Competitive salary and benefits
• Interesting international projects
• Opportunities for professional and career growth
• Opportunities to develop and learn advanced technologies
• Regular training and development opportunities
• Use of high-valued tools and applications

Apply now
